data.description: Step into contemporary elegance with this stucco gem on a corner lot. Sustainable living meets style with RV parking, xeriscape landscaping, solar panels, and a Tesla-ready EV charging station. Inside, enjoy LVP flooring, a chef's kitchen, and a master suite with a walk-in closet. Located near top-tier schools in sought-after Reno, it's not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Schedule a viewing today and let this eco-conscious oasis redefine modern living. Your dream home awaits!
